{"article_id":"AfAzYqn2YCdTUz9l","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The death of Jamal Khashoggi , the writer and activist","depth":12},{"id":1,"text":"who was killed in the Saudi Consulate in Turkey last month ,","depth":12},{"id":2,"text":"came at the directive of Saudi Crown Prince Mohammed bin Salman","depth":12},{"id":3,"text":"( MBS ) ,","depth":12},{"id":4,"text":"the CIA has determined","depth":10},{"id":5,"text":"according to a report out Friday .","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"The agency ' s conclusion came as a result of \" an understanding","depth":11},{"id":7,"text":"of how Saudi Arabia works , \"","depth":11},{"id":8,"text":"rather than a \" smoking gun , \"","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"a U.S. official with knowledge of the situation told The Wall Street Journal .","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"Khashoggi ' s death \" would not and could not have happened \"","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"if MBS was not connected ,","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"an official told the outlet .","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"The CIA did not offer a comment on the story","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"when contacted by Fox News .","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"The story was first reported by The Washington Post .","depth":5},{"id":16,"text":"Separately , a government official told Fox News","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"that the Khashoggi assessment is not a public document ,","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"and is not aware of plans","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"to make it public .","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"The official said","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"the intelligence has been briefed at very senior levels .","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"The revelation comes a day after Foreign Minister Adel al-Jubeir insisted","depth":4},{"id":23,"text":"that the crown prince did not play a role in the Washington Post columnist ' s death .","depth":4},{"id":24,"text":"TREASURY SLAPS SANCTIONS ON SAUDI OFFICIALS OVER DEATH OF JAMAL KHASHOGGI","depth":4},{"id":25,"text":"`` Absolutely , his royal highness the crown prince has nothing to do with this issue , ''","depth":6},{"id":26,"text":"he told reporters .","depth":6},{"id":27,"text":"MBS has also \" denied any knowledge \" of the circumstances","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"that led to Khashoggi ' s disappearance ,","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"President Trump said .","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"\" Just spoke with the Crown Prince of Saudi Arabia","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"who totally denied","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"any knowledge","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"of what took place in their Turkish Consulate , \"","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"the president tweeted on Oct. 16 .","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"News of the CIA 's findings comes","depth":5},{"id":36,"text":"one day after the Treasury Department announced","depth":6},{"id":37,"text":"they were sanctioning 17 Saudi government officials over Khashoggi ' s death .","depth":6},{"id":38,"text":"`` These individuals","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"who targeted and brutally killed a journalist","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"who resided and worked in the United States","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"must face consequences for their actions , ''","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"Treasury Secretary Steven Mnuchin said in a statement .","depth":6},{"id":43,"text":"`` The United States continues to diligently work","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"to ascertain all of the facts","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"and will hold accountable each of those","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"we find responsible","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"in order to achieve justice for Khashoggi ' s fiancée , children , and the family","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"he leaves behind . \"","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"SAUDI ARABIA INDICTS 11 ,","depth":3},{"id":50,"text":"SEEKS DEATH PENALTY FOR 5 , IN JAMAL KHASHOGGI ' S MURDER","depth":3},{"id":51,"text":"21 people are in custody ,","depth":5},{"id":52,"text":"the Saudis said .","depth":5},{"id":53,"text":"And the country ' s top prosecutor revealed","depth":5},{"id":54,"text":"that he would seek the death penalty for five of them .","depth":5},{"id":55,"text":"Saudi Arabia previously claimed","depth":5},{"id":56,"text":"that Khashoggi was killed in a fight .","depth":5},{"id":57,"text":"\" Discussions between citizen Jamal Khashoggi and those","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"who met him","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"while he was in the Saudi Consulate in Istanbul","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"led to a brawl and a physical altercation ,","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"which led to his death , \"","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"Saudi Arabia 's attorney general said in a statement ,","depth":6},{"id":63,"text":"according to The Wall Street Journal .","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":127,"left":112,"right":126,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":112,"left":87,"right":111,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":87,"left":85,"right":86,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":85,"left":79,"right":84,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":79,"left":78,"right":15,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":78,"left":76,"right":77,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":76,"left":73,"right":75,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":73,"left":69,"right":72,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":69,"left":68,"right":5,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":68,"left":67,"right":4,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":67,"left":65,"right":66,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":65,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":66,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"restatement","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":72,"left":71,"right":9,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":71,"left":70,"right":8,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":70,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":75,"left":74,"right":12,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":74,